    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = v0
    tmp = tmp
    v0 = 0.53
    v0 = wp.cos(0.37)
    v1 = ((0.01 / (tmp + 0.40 - tmp + 0.19)) + (tmp * (v2 + 0.05 + v0 + 0.45)))

    v1 = tmp
